We uploaded a very simple

00:10:23.436 --> 00:10:25.548
perceived temperature calculator

00:10:25.548 --> 00:10:26.540
where you can check out

00:10:26.540 --> 00:10:27.955
about your outdoor comfort.

00:10:27.955 --> 00:10:31.427
And I also hope that you

00:10:31.427 --> 00:10:32.749
share the idea that

